data.description: Come check out this stunning home in beautiful Lakewood Estates located just a few blocks from Cooper West Elementary. This 2 story home has 5 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, an office that could double as a 6th bedroom and a dining room that leads into the spacious kitchen perfect for hosting! The living room has new vinyl plank floors, surround sound and a gas fireplace. Upstairs has 4 large bedrooms and a quaint sitting area at the top of the stairs. Outdoors is a haven with a covered patio, storage shed, and extended parking with enough space for RV or boat parking.
